WEBVTT

00:04.172 --> 00:05.806
CHRIS ROCK:
Most days at school

00:05.839 --> 00:07.075
were usually the same.

00:07.108 --> 00:09.043
I got there at the same time,

00:09.077 --> 00:10.578
I saw the same kids.
Hey, Chris.

00:10.611 --> 00:11.579
Hey, Greg.

00:11.612 --> 00:13.814
Hey, Ebony.

00:13.847 --> 00:16.150
Ivory.

00:16.184 --> 00:18.352
And I took the same classes
with the same teachers.

00:18.386 --> 00:19.820
So did you hear?

00:19.853 --> 00:22.223
Ms. Morello's gonna be gone for,
like, two or three weeks.

00:22.256 --> 00:23.391
What?

00:23.424 --> 00:24.758
Yeah. She went
on a trip to Africa

00:24.792 --> 00:26.527
to help fight off an outbreak
of yellow fever.

00:26.560 --> 00:29.363
It was more like she went
to Harlem to fight off

00:29.397 --> 00:30.764
an outbreak of jungle fever.

00:35.236 --> 00:38.372
* Get your groove on,
get your groove on *

00:38.406 --> 00:39.507
* Come on...

00:39.540 --> 00:41.409
With Ms. Morello gone,

00:41.442 --> 00:44.412
we had every kind of substitute
imaginable.

00:44.445 --> 00:45.713
We had out-of-work actors...

00:45.746 --> 00:49.150
:
"To be... or not to be.

00:49.183 --> 00:52.286
That... is the question."

00:52.320 --> 00:54.788
...we had out-of-work
dancers...

00:57.458 --> 00:59.493
Can one of you kids get that
bucket of water

00:59.527 --> 01:01.695
and throw it on me?

01:01.729 --> 01:05.466
...and, sometimes, we had
out-of-work teachers.

01:07.301 --> 01:10.138
Enjoy this while you still can,

01:10.171 --> 01:14.475
'cause, believe me, it's all
downhill from here.

01:14.508 --> 01:16.644
We'd had just about every type
of sub we could think of...

01:18.179 --> 01:20.148
...except one-- a black sub.

01:20.181 --> 01:22.783
Good morning. I'm Mr. Newton.

01:22.816 --> 01:24.518
More like Mr. Tibbs.

01:24.552 --> 01:25.586
What's your name?

01:25.619 --> 01:27.188
Joey Caruso.

01:27.221 --> 01:28.789
And you're making fun of
me because I'm black?

01:28.822 --> 01:30.491
Yeah, you big dummy.

01:30.524 --> 01:31.492
He does it
to me every day.

01:31.525 --> 01:32.660
No, sir.

01:32.693 --> 01:33.861
Sounds like it to me.

01:33.894 --> 01:35.263
Sorry.

01:35.296 --> 01:37.131
If you want to make fun
of me, fine.

01:37.165 --> 01:39.667
But make fun of me for what
I do, not how I look.

01:39.700 --> 01:41.269
You don't see me
making fun of you

01:41.302 --> 01:43.771
because you look like
a Brooklyn Beach
Barney Rubble.

01:45.306 --> 01:47.475
No, sir.

01:47.508 --> 01:51.679
This black sub is
a bad mother...
* Shut your mouth!

01:51.712 --> 02:01.755
Captioning sponsored by
CBS PARAMOUNT NETWORK
